Hi, how can I contact support about ads that seem mistakenly flagged?

You can contact our Ad Support team by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com. They will be able to assist you with any issues regarding ads that may have been mistakenly flagged. Make sure to provide them with all relevant details about your ad for a quicker resolution.
